[b]Wait Arham, how did you get those case numbers?[/b]

Well, if you take a look at the methods, you see those numbers as option, option2, and option3.

<blockquote>public void options3(String option, String option2, String option3){ //3
		c.getCS().sendFrame126("Select an Option", 2470);
		c.getCS().sendFrame126([b]option[/b], [b]2471[/b]);
		c.getCS().sendFrame126([b]option2[/b], [b]2472[/b]);
		c.getCS().sendFrame126([b]option3[/b], [b]2473[/b]);
		c.getCS().sendFrame164(2469);
	}</blockquote>

[b]bold[/b] = Option int
[b]red[/b] = The option int (otherwise known as your option)'s place.

